<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<span class="bold">Elaine Equi</span> has published six collections of poetry, including <i>The Corner of the Mouth</i> (1986) and <i>Surface Tension</i> (1989). She was raised in the suburbs of Chicago, and now lives and teaches in New York City. Photograph of Elaine Equi copyright &#169; John Tranter 1989<br />
<br />
</p></td></tr></table></div>

